OL,6,FA Boots employee gave himself hundreds
OL,7,Fof advantage points, as well as
OL,8,Fstealing thousands from the tills and
OL,9,Fuploading bogus gift cards.
OL,11,FHamza Imran, 26, was caught out by an
OL,12,Finternal audit after almost a year of
OL,13,Fdefrauding the company. The audit
OL,14,Frevealed he had uploaded over 500
OL,15,Fadvantage points to his own card, as
OL,16,Fwell as pocketing money from the tills.
OL,18,FHe had also uploaded bogus John Lewis
OL,19,Fgift cards, totalling over #3,000,
OL,20,FManchester Minshull Street Crown Court
OL,21,Fheard.
