OL,3,CBoots worker gave himself points and
OL,4,Cused #3,000 of bogus vouchers
OL,6,FAn internal investigation was launched
OL,7,Fby the store which revealed he had
OL,8,Fuploaded 589 points to his own Boots
OL,9,FAdvantage card. The points can be used
OL,10,Fto spend within stores across the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FFurther investigations and CCTV
OL,14,Fexaminations showed that he uploaded
OL,15,FJohn Lewis gift cards at their limit
OL,16,Famount, to a total of #3,592.
