OL,6,F"As a result he started giving that
OL,7,Fmale the money," he said. "He was
OL,8,Fstruggling financially and continued
OL,9,Fuploading the advantage card points."
OL,11,FMr Sinker said Imran did not report
OL,12,Fmatters to the police at the time. He
OL,13,Falso said he'd come to the UK in 2023,
OL,14,Fobtained a degree in finance at Sussex
OL,15,FUniversity, and was a man of good
OL,16,Fprevious character.
OL,18,F"You said this has had a salutary
OL,19,Faffect on you," said Judge Joanne
OL,20,FWoodward.
