OL,6,F"You claim that you were threatened
OL,7,Fand coerced, but the fact is that your
OL,8,Fcriminality continued for a period
OL,9,Fshort of 12 months. You had the
OL,10,Fopportunity to extricate yourself in
OL,11,Fone way or another."
OL,13,FShe added that Imran had admitted
OL,14,Fbenefitted from the theft.
OL,16,F"You were given a high degree of trust
OL,17,Fby reason of your position," she said.
OL,19,FImran, of Redmires Court, Salford, was
OL,20,Fhanded eight months suspended for 18
OL,21,Fmonths, and 100 hours unpaid work.
